edu.cmu.lti.f14.hw3.hw3_carolche.utils

Class Ranking

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.lti.f14.hw3.hw3_carolche.utils.Ranking
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Ranking>

    public class Ranking
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Ranking>
    Ranking class is for making ranking of documents by cosine similarity. In order to create a Ranking object, cosine similarity, relevance and text of documents are needed.
    Author:
    Carol Cheng

        public int compareTo(Ranking otherRanking)
